site-address: The Mill Site, Dane Street, Bishop's Stortford, CM23 3XZ
ownership: not owned by a public authority
notes: The Mill Site has been allocated in the emerging East Herts District Plan, under Policy BISH10. A housing allocation has not been given for this site, as currently the site is still in employment use. The site will remain a designated employment area, until such time that the land becomes available for redevelopment.
